### Health Check
GET http://localhost:5000/health

### Create Book
POST http://localhost:5000/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Node.js Design Patterns",
  "author": "Mario Casciaro",
  "isbn": "9781839214110",
  "genre": "Programming",
  "publisher": "Packt",
  "publicationYear": 2022,
  "totalCopies": 8,
  "availableCopies": 8,
  "shelfLocation": "D1-R4",
  "bookType": "Circulating",
  "status": "Available"
}

### Get All Books
GET http://localhost:5000/books

### Get Book By ID
GET http://localhost:5000/books/{{bookId}}

### Update Book
PUT http://localhost:5000/books/{{bookId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "availableCopies": 5,
  "status": "Checked Out"
}

### Delete Book
DELETE http://localhost:5000/books/{{bookId}}

### Search By Title
GET http://localhost:5000/books/search?title=Node

### Search By Author
GET http://localhost:5000/books/search?author=Martin
